{
  "stem": "10829.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's where the hides and furs was made and processed for all around that area.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were sort of, quote, 'bootleg' hide makers, as part from, because you had all this cattle.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was-- when we-- Mother opened up the cellar, there was already two people sitting there, and there was room for two barrels, and then you had-- in the sides, you know how a barrel is round.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were two people down there, and there was only room for one person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my sister-- she put my sister in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the only place I could-- and I-- I still scream about it whenever I think about it-- and she threw me in a barrel of-- of lime, and she covered us back up.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She put a table on top of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then she and my brother hid under-- hid in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They hid in a closet what they had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was under the foundation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was-- right near the foundation, you tear-- you put a-- most of them were dirt floors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she dug it out, and then she climbed down underneath there, and that's where they hid, there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So Mom and my brother was hidden there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we laid down there, it seemed like eternity, but my sister and I and the other two people were-- no, actually, three people.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were three people there and my sister, and there were five of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we laid down there three days and four nights, yeah, because it was early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- then and four nights, we laid there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother was with my brother there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the only thing we had for all of us was one potato.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then that's all we lived on.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
